# Tradolog

Tradolog is a premium Trading Journal SaaS.

Tech Stack

- Astro 7
- React
- Tailwind CSS v4
- shadcn/ui
- PostgreSQL
- Drizzle ORM
- Better Auth
- Cloudflare R2

Always use Feature Based Architecture.

Always use Strict TypeScript.

Never use any.

Always use Repository Pattern.

Always use Service Layer.

Never mix business logic with UI.

Always use reusable components.

Always use Zod validation.

Always use React Hook Form.

Use UUID.

Every table has

- id
- created_at
- updated_at
- deleted_at

Deploy target

- Vercel